<h2 class="bold font-l">Andre the Giant Heel Turn</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Documentary clip tells the story of Andre the Giant's Heel Turn against Hulk Hogan before Wrestlemania III. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FaceHeelTurn" class='trope-example-link'>FaceHeel Turn</a></p>
